high_descs: Turn and face the counter on the right.
Pick up the ladle from the front of the counter.
Carry the ladle and take a step to the left.
Open the left middle drawer and place the ladle inside. Shut the drawer.
Take a step to the right and look at the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the right side of the counter.
Carry the ladle and take a step to the left.
Open the middle left drawer and place the ladle inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two ladles to a drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward to the counter.
Pick up the large spoon that is closest to you on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right, go forward, turn around to the drawers beneath the counter.
Open the left middle drawer, put the spoon inside.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the left, go to the counter.
Pick up the large spoon that is on the counter in front of the bread.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right, go forward, turn around to the drawers beneath the counter.
Open the left middle drawer, put the spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the ladle near the edge of the counter.
Move over to the left of the counter
Place the ladle in the second drawer on the left.
Move over right to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the ladle on next to the stove.
Move over to the left of the counter again.
Place the ladle behind the first ladle in the second drawer on the left.
anns.task_desc: Move the ladles from the counter to the drawers
